**Count**

## Examples

```csharp
//If there are less than 365 bars on the chart, text indicates how many bars are on the chart
if (Count < 365)
{
  Draw.TextFixed(this, "tag1", "There are " + Count + " bars on the chart", TextPosition.BottomRight);
